---
title: Tandoori Inspired Chicken Tikka Masala with Spinach and Garlic Butter Rice
description: Indulge in some nostalgia with a classic from childhood that's also child-friendly! This Tandoori Inspired Chicken Tikka Masala is a grown-up version of the much-loved takeaway dish. For little ones, go easy on the tandoori masala mix to keep it mild.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W13_UK_F17608-2_MAIN_low-04ea729c.jpg
